title: Beach with sea stack and bright sun
description: A sandy beach with a large sea stack on the left, people along the shoreline, and a bright sun/cloud glare in the upper-right of the image.

title: Snowy mountain range with sun
description: Snow-covered mountains under a clear blue sky with the sun visible near the top-left.

title: Snowy mountain trail with sun
description: A snowy mountain trail and densely forested slopes under a clear blue sky. The bright sun is visible near the upper center, casting light and lens flare over the scene.

title: Sun and textured cloud sky
description: Bright sun amid extensive altocumulus clouds over silhouetted mountains and rooftop skyline.

title: Sunset pasture with grazing animals
description: A grassy pastoral landscape at sunset with the sun low in the left sky, a line of trees on the horizon, a farmhouse, and grazing sheep/cattle in the midground.

title: Road at sunset with bicycle handlebars
description: A cyclist's view along a road at sunset. The sun is low on the left, casting glare across fields; bicycle handlebars and a bike computer are visible in the lower foreground.

title: Beach shoreline with people
description: Sandy beach in the foreground with people and small groups near the waterline; sunlit ocean and blue sky with thin clouds in the background.

title: Sunset over dock
description: Sun setting over calm water with a wooden dock in the foreground and posts to the right.

title: Foggy path with tree and sun
description: A misty landscape with a single large tree near the center, a cyclist on a paved path leading toward the tree, and the sun visible through the fog near the top of the image.

title: Mountain valley with winding road
description: A green mountain valley with a winding road leading toward cloudy peaks. Low clouds obscure the mountain tops; no sun is visible in the scene.

title: Sunset over rocky beach
description: Sun setting over the ocean with clouds above and rocks on the beach in the foreground.

title: Sun over pool with palm trees
description: Bright sun near the top-center behind silhouetted palm trees, with its reflection visible on the pool surface in the lower half of the image.

title: Lighthouse at sunset
description: A coastal scene showing a lighthouse on a cliff at sunset with the sun low in the sky to the left of the lighthouse and calm water to the right.

title: Sunrise over misty hills
description: Warm sunrise casting light over misty rolling hills and bare trees, sun visible at the right edge of the scene.

title: Sunset on bridge with cyclist
description: Sun setting over a riverside bridge walkway with a cyclist heading toward the sun; calm water reflects the light.

title: Sunset picnic under a tree
description: A low sunset over a grassy field with an olive tree in the foreground. In the lower foreground is a woven table surface with plates, bowls and a beer bottle, and the sun is visible near the horizon to the right of the tree.

title: Sunrise over Beach
description: Calm ocean at sunrise with a bright sun near the horizon and rocky foreground along the beach.

title: Misty mountain landscape
description: Panoramic view of layered mountains with morning mist and a pale, cloudy sky. Foreground hills and tree-covered slopes transition into distant ridgelines under soft blue-gray light.

title: Snowy mountain with sun
description: Snow-covered slope and distant mountains under a bright sun in a hazy sky.

title: Sunset through rainy windshield
description: View through a rain-speckled window showing a low sun (or bright reflections) near a bridge/structure at the lower center; sky is overcast and water droplets are visible on the glass.

title: Sunset road with trees and mountains
description: A curving road descending toward a valley with trees in the foreground and mountains in the distance; the sun is visible above the treeline casting long shadows across the pavement.

title: Sunlit mountain road
description: A winding road with a guardrail curves through a wooded hillside toward distant layered mountains under a pale blue sky. The sun is visible through the trees at the upper-left, casting long shadows across the pavement.

title: Sunlit mountain road
description: Curving mountain road with low sun near the upper-left, casting long shadows; clear blue sky and ridgeline visible.

title: Dam wall with sun and vegetation
description: A large concrete dam fills most of the frame with vegetation in the foreground and the sun visible near the top-left, producing lens flare.

title: Mountain valley with sun glare
description: A wide mountain valley with a winding road and grassy slopes; the sun and lens flare appear in the top-left.

title: Sunset over city with bicycle
description: View from a hillside overlooking a town at sunset. A bicycle is visible in the foreground on a railing, with the sun near the upper-right sky casting an orange haze over distant hills and the city below.

title: Snowy road under a bright sun
description: A wide winter landscape with snow-covered fields, a winding road in the foreground and a bright sun in a clear blue sky.

title: Lighthouse at Sunset
description: A lighthouse on a rocky shore with the sun low in the sky to the upper right and the ocean visible along the horizon.

title: Sunset over calm water
description: A warm orange sunset with the sun setting near distant hills and its reflection on a calm body of water.

title: Snowy mountain slope with sun
description: A bright winter scene showing a snow-covered slope with ski/snow tracks leading up to a tree-lined ridge on the right. The sun is low over the distant mountains on the left under a clear blue sky.

title: Sun over mountains
description: Landscape with the sun in the upper-left above rolling hills and vegetation. Foreground shows shrubs and a curved retaining wall at bottom-right; winding road visible in the valley. Clear blue sky with some clouds and lens flare from the sun.

title: Sunset with Horses
description: Landscape photo at sunset with the sun low in the sky near center-right, silhouetted horses on a small ridge, trees and a mountain in the background, and a road in the foreground.
